AIs favorite scale


31 Dec 2020 02:21






I noticed the melody wasn't in any conventional key signatures, So I tried to look up what scale it is. The notes shown in chromatic order are: C, C#, F, G, A#, and B. Starting from C, the scale would Half step, Major 3rd, Whole step, Minor 3rd, Half step, Half step. allthescales.org lists it as the 16th 6-note scale Pothimic mode. Congrats on sending me on a scavenger hunt. +1







